Package graph

Interface Graphs

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    Graph, GraphAbs
    public interface Graphs
    Interface class that describes a graph composed by weighted edges and nodes
    Author:
    John Mendonça, Manuel Domingues, Rúben Gomes
